    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are cooking, add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti</strong> to a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>spaghetti</strong> for 2-3 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>spaghetti </strong>and return to the pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> spinach</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
