    {
      "instruction": "<p>Turn the heat down to medium-high and add your <strong>creamy single soy</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until the spinach has wilted and the sauce has slightly thickened</p><p>Season with a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>plant-based</strong> <strong>creamy mushroom sauce</strong></p>",
