    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked spaghetti </strong>to the <strong>plant-based</strong> <strong>creamy mushroom sauce</strong> and stir everything together – this is your <strong>plant-based creamy mushroom spaghetti</strong></p>",
